  "plot outline": "James Bond 007 is Britain's top agent, and is on an exciting mission, to solve the mysterious murder of a fellow agent. The task sends him to Jamaica, where he joins forces with Quarrel and a loyal C.I.A. Agent, Felix Leiter. While dodging tarantulas, \"fire breathing dragons\", and a trio of assassins, known as \"the three blind mice\". Bond meets up with the beautiful Honey Ryder and goes face to face with the evil Dr. No.",
